    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>I think what you're after is <code>\\Q$5\\E</code>.  Also see <code>Pattern.quote(s)</code> introduced in Java5.</p>\n\n<p>See <a href=\"http://java.sun.com/javase/6/docs/api/java/util/regex/Pattern.html\" rel=\"noreferrer\">Pattern</a> javadoc for details.</p>\n"
