      "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
      "body" : "Specifically, <code>Pattern.quote</code> replaces special characters in regex search strings, like .|+() etc, and <code>Matcher.quoteReplacement</code> replaces special characters in replacement strings, like \\1 for backreferences."
