      "comment_id" : 45093360,
      "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
      "body" : "Matcher.quoteReplacement(&quot;4$&amp;%$&quot;) produces &quot;4\\$&amp;%\\$&quot;. It escapes the special characters."
