      "body" : "Awesome. Here is an example where we want to replace <code>$Group$</code> with <code>T$UYO$HI</code>. The <code>$</code> symbol is special both in the pattern and in the replacement: <code>&quot;$Group$ Members&quot;.replaceFirst(Pattern.quote(&quot;$Group$&quot;), Matcher.quoteReplacement(&quot;T$UYO$HI&quot;))</code>"
