      "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
      "body" : "Small typo, big consequences: &quot;([^a-zA-z0-9])&quot; does also not match (i.e. not escape) [, \\, ], ^ which you certainly want to have escaped! The typo is the second &#39;z&#39; which should be a &#39;Z&#39;, otherwise everything from ASCII 65 to ASCII 122 is included"
